By Andile Mngxitama The irony of SA: Major 1 is responding to the oppressor by any means necessary like a real revolutionary rebel, on the other side the people who claim to be revolutionaries are behaving like colonized Christians. Metlholo… Time to learn the Hokma Wisdom… It’s the revolutionary way! Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.